snippet.title: Doki Doki Metal Club: Official Trailer [OUT NOW]
snippet.description:
Will you shred your way into her heart?
DOWNLOAD NOW: https://www.mediafire.com/file/xnxu70j89yxb339/dokidokimetalclub.rar/file

Doki Doki Metal Club is a story of a high school club of metalheads. Instead of literature, this time it's music that the girls are passionate about. MC, a poser listening to metalcore, joins a club where every member has a different taste in metal. Yuri, a metal elitist, is a fan of "true metal" and all things kvlt. She introduces MC to the world of black metal.

Music: Amon Amarth - War of the Gods
